---
const ornament = `╔══════════════════════════════════╗
║   FIELD STATION · TN-37821       ║
║   35.9670° N    83.1879° W       ║
║   ELEV 1,063 ft  ·  KN4ABK       ║
╚══════════════════════════════════╝`;
---

<div class="about-grid">
  <div class="about-prose">
    <p>
      I'm a first-generation scientist from Appalachia. I spent my first
      career building production ML systems; I'm now matriculating to LSU
      to read physics, with a transfer target of <strong>MIT, Cornell, or Caltech</strong>
      for fall 2027.
    </p>
    <p>
      The work here sits at the seam between three disciplines that
      are usually kept apart: <strong>quantum computation, gravitational-wave
      astronomy, and embodied artificial intelligence</strong>. I think the
      interesting physics happens at that seam.
    </p>
    <p>
      I also build the instruments. The lab has an MPCVD reactor for
      NV-center diamond, a Paul trap, a 4-metre L-band interferometer,
      a chalcogenide memristor reservoir, and an Earth-field NMR rig
      — all assembled and characterised on-site.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="about-stats">
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">3</span><span class="stat-label">Years prod ML</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">7</span><span class="stat-label">Active rigs</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">3</span><span class="stat-label">Languages spoken</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">17</span><span class="stat-label">Onyx, in cat-years</span></div>
    </div>

    <pre class="ornament" aria-hidden="true">{ornament}</pre>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .about-prose {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--bone);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .about-prose p + p { margin-top: 1.4em; }
  .about-prose strong { color: var(--phosphor); font-weight: 400; }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--rule);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .stat {
    background: var(--ink-2);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--bone);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bone-faint);
  }

  .ornament {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--phosphor-d);
    line-height: 1.2;
    opacity: 0.75;
    white-space: pre;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
</style>
